data.label: openai_chat_completion
data.docstring:
Make a chat completion request to OpenAI.

Args:
    model (str): The OpenAI model to use.
    messages (list[dict[str, str | dict[str, str]]]): The messages to send to the model.
    base_url (str, optional): The base URL for the OpenAI API. Defaults to "https://api.openai.com/v1".
    api_key_variable (str, optional): The environment variable containing the API key. Defaults to "OPENAI_API_KEY".

Returns:
    dict[str, Any]: The OpenAI response.

data.label: get_openai_message_content
data.docstring:
Extract the message content from the OpenAI response.

Args:
    response (dict[str, Any]): The OpenAI response.

Returns:
    str: The message content.

data.label: View
data.value: In a medium, full shot, a brown bear with its mouth slightly open, is walking along the shore of a pond, looking out toward the viewer. The bear is centrally located, but most of its body reaches the left edge of the frame. Its thick, coarse fur is dark brown on its legs and stomach, and lighter golden-brown on its back, head, and around its small, rounded ears. On its shoulders is a dark-brown hump of fur. The bear's snout is lengthy and projects from its head, and its nose is black. The bear is walking toward the lower-right edge of the frame, alongside a mossy green pond. Tall blades of green grass grow on the grassy bank in the bottom-left corner and along the right side of the pond. Some of the blades of grass contain small purple flowers. The background consists of the pond's green, sunlit water. Small insects are visible as white specks flying above the water's surface, on the upper-left side. A red object floats on the water in the middle-right of the frame. The lighting enters the scene from the upper left, making the bear's fur glow.
